OL,5, Former Antiques Roadshow expert Henry  
OL,6, Sandon has died at the age of 95.      
OL,8,FHis son John confirmed he died         
OL,9,Fpeacefully at a care home in Malvern,  
OL,10,FWorcestershire, on Christmas morning.  
OL,12,FAppointed curator of the Dyson Perrins 
OL,13,FMuseum at the Royal Worcester factory  
OL,14,Fin 1967, Sandon joined BBC One's       
OL,15,FAntiques Roadshow in 1979.             
OL,17,FJohn Sandon, who too became a face on  
OL,18,Fthe show, said his father was like a   
OL,19,F"favourite uncle" to those who tuned in
OL,20,Feach week.                             
